    "title": "Accommodation at Casa Petri Rosia Montana",
    "description": "Stay in a heritage house from the Historic Center of Roșia Montana, recently renovated with bathrooms and kitchen access. See also the hiking and bike trails to discover our area: roman galleries, gold mining industry, heritage buildings, mountains, lakes and many more. Rosia Montana, Alba, Apuseni Mountains, Transylvania - Romania.",
