    {
      "type": "articles",
      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "title": "",
          "textContent": "Casa Petri is situated in the Historic Center of Rosia Montana and is a heritage building where we preserved the traditional style like the wooden floor, the windows or the heating with terracotta stoves, but were we added modern facilities like the bathrooms and the kitchen. There are many cosy spots around the house, a green yard with a nice view to the Cânic peak, <i class='fa fa-wifi'></i> <b>free wifi</b>, board games and parking spots."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "articles",
      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "title": "'Books' room",
          "textContent": "The downstairs room has one meter wide walls built out of rocks and a closet filled with books. It has private bathroom, two bunk beds and an expandable couch. <br><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i> <i class='fa fa-arrows-h''></i> <i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i>",
          "images": [
            {
              "text": "<b>'Books' room</b> - here you can find ‘the cupboard with books’ - a cupboard transformed into a library where you can find old books and board games.",
              "thumbnailUrl": "img/accommodation/article/rooms/room1/thumbnail/1.jpg",
              "fullSizeUrl": "img/accommodation/article/rooms/room1/fullSize/1.jpg"
            },
            {
              "text": "<b>'Books' room - inside</b> -  In the showcase are old photos from Roșia, crystal clusters rocks from the roman gallery and old objects used in the household.",
              "thumbnailUrl": "img/accommodation/article/rooms/room1/thumbnail/2.jpg",
              "fullSizeUrl": "img/accommodation/article/rooms/room1/fullSize/2.jpg"
            },
            {
              "text": "<b>'Books' room - bathroom</b> - Heating with electric boiler",
              "thumbnailUrl": "img/accommodation/article/rooms/room1/thumbnail/3.jpg",
              "fullSizeUrl": "img/accommodation/article/rooms/room1/fullSize/3.jpg"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
