        {
          "title": "",
          "textContent": "Because we also love to go camping, we prepared a small camping place in our yard, for maximum 4 tents, with bathroom, kitchen, dinning area, gazebo, hammocks, <i class='fa fa-wifi'></i> <b>free wifi</b> and electricity.",
