    {
      "type": "title",
      "text": "<i class='fa fa-cutlery'></i> Food",
      "sectionId": "food",
      "addLinkInPageHeadline": true
    },
    {
      "type": "articles",
      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "textContent": "We have a kitchen with dishes, refrigerator, stove and microwave where you can cook, or, if you wish, we can order food from a local restaurant. Our recommendation is to eat homemade meals at local farm (~10min away by foot), but please inform us when you book a room, or as early as possible, to make the reservations. There are also 3 grocery stores around the house (~5min away).",
