      "type": "articles",
      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "textContent": "In order to have everything set for your arrival, please make an early reservation. Here you can book or see the cost of the rooms, camping or bicycles. If you want guided trails we will respond by email with the cost (it depends upon the selected trails and the size of the group). For larger groups or longer periods we can offer discounts."
